{"tid":2079141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線】日本戰線比熱狗（尿狗）搞到臭晒","createTime":"2020-06-25T14:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T02:14:35.000Z","uid":278414,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c667b4d50ea743dcbf67c53e288d9dc28967fee","tid":2079141,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"大家可以追番小弟前兩個POST先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n①【國際戰線】平野鈴子小姐起Twitter同分化5毛開片<br />\n&darr;　&darr;　&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072403\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072403</a><br />\n<br />\n②【國際戰線】原來之前跟平野鈴子小姐起Twitter開片嘅5毛同（熱狗？）又關<br />\n&darr;    &darr;    &darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2074597\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2074597</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼上次熱狗被手足踢爆主動提供黑材料比5毛後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事源者熱狗「魯芬」自鎖acc縮咗入龜殼不見天日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其後手足再報料，發現有熱狗繼續重施故技賣港，言無論次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中發現熱狗原來對「飲尿」情有獨鍾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1275710480884039682?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1275710480884039682%3Fs%3D21&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=c60c95d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1275710480884039682%3Fs%3D21&h=9f8e876d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1275710480884039682?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n事件爆發後有國際戰線嘅手足整左meme圖諷刺熱狗<br />\n&darr;  &darr;  &darr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygjr1Mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fygjr1Mx.jpg&h=d175ccf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有其他手足主動追擊班拖後腿嘅熱狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/randolphcjpn/status/1276056259247001602?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frandolphcjpn%2Fstatus%2F1276056259247001602%3Fs%3D21&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=1600c51a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frandolphcjpn%2Fstatus%2F1276056259247001602%3Fs%3D21&h=a4108a40\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/randolphcjpn/status/1276056259247001602?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際戰線一直決人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現在仲要有班死熱狗做埋晒仆街嘢，多埋個「內患」......唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16052a2c97b38457842c93eb6ef57dc67df5cc4","tid":2079141,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee8c55f4f17ba200439b66efb6d2669fdb06d701","tid":2079141,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc7735adabdf04a51c793ce59bc0b1347d6067a","tid":2079141,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"588f8bf3b0cf6706d5f7b3ed24c063b8fc5550c1","tid":2079141,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91b2b0c03d130c16c7d89bec994c08195f6b92ac","tid":2079141,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"之前係twitter 見到某會員搶晒日本戰線手足功勞...屌"},{"pid":"56464861497b0cebb61a8ab9a3727cbe6c21d6